  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300174383_39_940-1035",
      "chapterUid": 39,
      "range": "940-1035",
      "markText": "其中最有趣的发现是，中国参与者对婚姻伴侣的贞洁特别重视。",
      "totalCount": 400,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300174383&chapterUid=39&rangeStart=940&rangeEnd=1035",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f9632d30813abaa9eg013699?chapterUid=39&rangeStart=940&rangeEnd=1035"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300174383_42_11365-11417",
      "chapterUid": 42,
      "range": "11365-11417",
      "markText": "自然选择只是对那些碰巧存活下来的遗传变异发挥作用。进化不是一个有目的的过程，更不会预知生物体未来的需要。",
      "totalCount": 377,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300174383&chapterUid=42&rangeStart=11365&rangeEnd=11417",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f9632d30813abaa9eg013699?chapterUid=42&rangeStart=11365&rangeEnd=11417"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300174383_47_60966-61054",
      "chapterUid": 47,
      "range": "60966-61054",
      "markText": "有时，这些男性满足于短期的性关系，不愿意给出长期的承诺，这就让女性面临一个难题。对于这个问题，解决手段之一是寻求对方的爱情。爱情往往标志着一个男性从事实上对某个女性作出了承诺。",
      "totalCount": 342,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300174383&chapterUid=47&rangeStart=60966&rangeEnd=61054",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f9632d30813abaa9eg013699?chapterUid=47&rangeStart=60966&rangeEnd=61054"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300174383_42_21709-21793",
      "chapterUid": 42,
      "range": "21709-21793",
      "markText": "假如你是一个基因，你会怎样来促进自己的复制？首先，你得保证你的宿主的生存。其次，你需要促使宿主繁殖。第三，你还可以帮助那些携带有你一部分基因拷贝的其他个体的生存和繁衍。",
      "totalCount": 324,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300174383&chapterUid=42&rangeStart=21709&rangeEnd=21793",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f9632d30813abaa9eg013699?chapterUid=42&rangeStart=21709&rangeEnd=21793"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300174383_42_60101-60148",
      "chapterUid": 42,
      "range": "60101-60148",
      "markText": "人可能与生俱来就已经拥有了某些预置程序或特定装备，规定了对某些特定信息做出反应而忽略其他信息。",
      "totalCount": 324,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300174383&chapterUid=42&rangeStart=60101&rangeEnd=60148",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f9632d30813abaa9eg013699?chapterUid=42&rangeStart=60101&rangeEnd=60148"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300174383_42_7646-7684",
      "chapterUid": 42,
      "range": "7646-7684",
      "markText": "达尔文有一个非常好的科学习惯，他很乐于关注那些看起来与他的理论不一致的证据。",
      "totalCount": 280,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300174383&chapterUid=42&rangeStart=7646&rangeEnd=7684",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f9632d30813abaa9eg013699?chapterUid=42&rangeStart=7646&rangeEnd=7684"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300174383_42_9551-9579",
      "chapterUid": 42,
      "range": "9551-9579",
      "markText": "在动物界中，绝大多数动物都是由雌性来挑选她们的潜在配偶。",
      "totalCount": 256,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300174383&chapterUid=42&rangeStart=9551&rangeEnd=9579",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f9632d30813abaa9eg013699?chapterUid=42&rangeStart=9551&rangeEnd=9579"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300174383_42_57058-57092",
      "chapterUid": 42,
      "range": "57058-57092",
      "markText": "即人类心理被设计出来是为了解决特殊的信息加工问题——生存和繁衍问题。",
      "totalCount": 255,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300174383&chapterUid=42&rangeStart=57058&rangeEnd=57092",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f9632d30813abaa9eg013699?chapterUid=42&rangeStart=57058&rangeEnd=57092"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300174383_42_18867-18901",
      "chapterUid": 42,
      "range": "18867-18901",
      "markText": "我们的认知和知觉范畴是先于个体经验而存在的，它们能够适应外部的环境。",
      "totalCount": 253,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300174383&chapterUid=42&rangeStart=18867&rangeEnd=18901",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f9632d30813abaa9eg013699?chapterUid=42&rangeStart=18867&rangeEnd=18901"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300174383_42_33381-33428",
